{"tid":1631935,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【經濟危機】港共最大既春袋","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:51.000Z","uid":235374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"551db1df62342ab29f8b76f2430b7a80b4877757","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:57.000Z","msg":"政府表示，有關社交媒體傳言指行政長官即將再根據「緊急法」宣布<span style=\"color: red;\">星期二及三停市，停工及停學</span>；並且<span style=\"color: red;\">凍結香港人的資產</span>，政府發言人澄清有關傳聞純屬謠言，絕非事實。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，政府考慮到目前公共安全受到廣泛危害的迫切情況，訂立《禁止蒙面規例》，以加強警隊執法和對意圖違法者產生阻嚇作用，遏止暴力，盡快讓香港社會回復平靜。這絕非隨意的做法，而是困難但必須的決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於有關<span style=\"color: red;\">金管局會訂立《提款法》限制市民每日提款金額的傳言</span>，金管局今日已經發表聲明，強調絕無此事。該局並指香港銀行體系十分穩健，銀行有充足流動資金應付市民的需要。<br />\n<br />\n發言人提醒市民要認清這些社交媒體謠傳的意圖，是製造恐慌，令香港社會陷入進一步混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e2edd0314391527dbdb67c5bc6462efca8aeb6","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急法就正正係焦土，大家文宣要將兩樣野連結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ba31c4fa194c829ff8ea3f83fd80a7ca743b1801","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家太過focus係蒙面法 裝修 私了 忽略左緊急法帶來既經濟危機 大家要明白呢一點 呢個係港共最大春袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"4eb2d93bec2879049bd68e263eeacc4f72e2df39","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"efa1448973bf94b628d434696295afe3ba26f399","tid":1631935,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3b2a58bdb7abb43940cfcb635908b50b1f1d6c","tid":1631935,"uid":154277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:07.000Z","msg":"一路都話 擠提先最有機會跪"},{"pid":"091547ff1c5a8e963098cf4dc00aae6c07963ed6","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b3b2a58bdb7abb43940cfcb635908b50b1f1d6c","tid":1631935,"uid":154277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:07.000Z","msg":"一路都話 擠提先最有機會跪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"大家要積極文宣緊急法既潛在危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係造謠ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763a2ad1a0bf65cfcbc18b150ccf2d5a7cd10bce","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊急法背後最痛既就係有無限想像 結合現在既社會狀況 都唔知會發生咩事...係我都換定美金...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"444df2804034522e0d9e9c3e2f5da1818ab43b3d","tid":1631935,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"87f19471b1040aafe202c70e2c6d6ec20892afcb","tid":1631935,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ddfe69ca7267761d5e362f6482d493328040c05","tid":1631935,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-0